Package: Spectral
Type: Package
Title: Classes and methods for spectral (optical) data
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-07-02
Author: Servet Ahmet Cizmeli
Maintainer: Servet Ahmet Cizmeli <sac@arctus.ca>
Description: This package provides S4 classes and methods for spectral data. Spectral data are regularly used in remote sensing, bio-optical oceanography and environmental and earth sciences. Any optical dataset that was colleced at a given wavelength of the radiative spectrum can be manipulated using tools offered in this package.
License: GPL
LazyLoad: yes